{
  "stem": "9963.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they opened the wagons every time, everywhere it came, about 40% of people were dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On this train, when finally we came to a Celle-- it was a city not far from Hanover in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The train stopped over there, and before you know, the American planes with the English planes-- all Allied planes-- came and start bombardment the train, from the last wagon to the first locomotive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We start jumping out from the train, because here people were-- were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I see that here, you know, the friend is bleeding and he's laying down and here, the, you know, people-- so we jumped out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The SS, were shooting to us, but we try to run away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But another five minutes, the plane is coming back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, they start bombarding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Finally, I was able to run away and hide in the bushes over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The planes came back the third time, but in the meantime, in that train was three wagons of bread-- with all kind of food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they didn't give it to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "For the-- like 10 days or more, we were on the train, we didn't have nothing what to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we ran to the train and we grabbed a couple loaves of bread and we ran away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I ran back, when the planes came and started bombardment, I got wounded over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got a bomb split, what I have here, see the hole in my shoulders.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't even know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't felt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to me, was just to catch that piece of bread, because we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I brought the bread, and the other my friends did also, and we divided.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
